♫ The light of the fireflies scatters away ♫

193
00:13:06,228 --> 00:13:10,548
♫ Swaying in the wind within wind ♫

194
00:13:10,548 --> 00:13:13,281
♫ The wind and the moon arrive
as promised on long nights ♫

195
00:13:13,281 --> 00:13:17,033
♫ Granting me dreams within dreams ♫

196
00:13:17,665 --> 00:13:20,289
♫ Words ready to be spoken
ultimately fall silent ♫

197
00:13:20,289 --> 00:13:24,161
♫ Reunite with you after lives apart ♫

198
00:13:24,161 --> 00:13:31,444
♫ Love and hate pass by in haste ♫

199
00:13:31,444 --> 00:13:38,401
♫ Winter has its arrival,
flowers have their withering ♫

200
00:13:38,401 --> 00:13:45,313
♫ The light in your eyes remains evergreen
through the years ♫

201
00:13:45,313 --> 00:13:52,481
♫ Just like the wind blows out the flames
into ashes ♫

202
00:13:52,481 --> 00:13:58,561
♫ Recognize you beneath your name ♫

203
00:13:58,561 --> 00:14:02,601
♫ Willing to write for you,
against the current ♫

204
00:14:03,732 --> 00:14:10,593
♫ Spring has the intention to come,
you have the intention to return ♫

205
00:14:10,593 --> 00:14:16,705
♫ Two flustered souls meet ♫

206
00:14:16,705 --> 00:14:20,329
♫ The foreshadowing has been set ♫
